cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "grouped-nf4-gemm: single-launch 4-bit codebook GEMM over fused MoE expert stacks"
abstract: >-
  A Triton kernel that runs the grouped expert GEMM directly on 4-bit-packed
  MoE weights (NF4 and native MXFP4), decoding the codebook in-register inside
  the mainloop with fp32 accumulation — no dequantize-then-matmul round trip.
authors:
